Machakos Governor Dr. Alfred Mutua and a section of Jubilee leaders have criticised Wiper leader Kalonzo Musyoka over his calls to have presidential term limits abolished accusing him of clawing back the democratic gains kenyans have made. Mutua is now calling on Kalonzo, to support the Maendeleo Chapchap leader’s 2022 presidential bid, maintaining there are clear indications the Wiper leader has abandoned his. 